name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Next.js Explorer - NextJS App & Pages Router

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Quickly check if a webpage is built with Next.js and explore static properties and other related NextJS useful metrics.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
For NextJS App Router & Pages Router.

Next.js Explorer is a browser extension for Google Chrome designed to help developers explore and visualize the structure and data of their Next.js applications.

Click the extension icon to explore Next.js client generated bundles.

Please, if something is wrong or the extension isn't working for you, contact me by opening a support ticket:

https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/iiekmbomdcmddchlplbdlkkpdgncgpdg/support?hl=ca
